2026-04-08 12:47:50.743 | INFO     | app.agent.toolcall:think:89 - 🔧 Tool arguments: {"code": "import requests\nimport xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\nfrom datetime import datetime\nimport json\n\n# 搜索RAG相关论文\nquery = \"RAG retrieval augmented generation\"\nurl = f\"http://export.arxiv.org/api/query?search_query=all:{query}&start=0&max_results=15&sortBy=submittedDate&sortOrder=descending\"\n\nprint(f\"正在搜索arXiv: {query}\")\nprint(\"=\" * 80)\n\ntry:\n    response = requests.get(url)\n    response.raise_for_status()\n    \n    # 解析XML响应\n    root = ET.fromstring(response.content)\n    \n    # 定义命名空间\n    ns = {\n        'atom': 'http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom',\n        'arxiv': 'http://arxiv.org/schemas/atom'\n    }\n    \n    papers = []\n    \n    for entry in root.findall('atom:entry', ns):\n        paper = {}\n        \n        # 提取标题\n        title_elem = entry.find('atom:title', ns)\n        paper['title'] = title_elem.text.strip() if title_elem is not None and title_elem.text else \"No title\"\n        \n        # 提取作者\n        authors = []\n        for author in entry.findall('atom:author', ns):\n            name_elem = author.find('atom:name', ns)\n            if name_elem is not None and name_elem.text:\n                authors.append(name_elem.text.strip())\n        paper['authors'] = authors\n        \n        # 提取摘要\n        summary_elem = entry.find('atom:summary', ns)\n        paper['abstract'] = summary_elem.text.strip() if summary_elem is not None and summary_elem.text else \"No abstract\"\n        \n        # 提取发布日期\n        published_elem = entry.find('atom:published', ns)\n        if published_elem is not None and published_elem.text:\n            published_date = published_elem.text[:10]  # 只取日期部分\n            paper['published'] = published_date\n        else:\n            paper['published'] = \"Unknown\"\n        \n        # 提取arXiv ID和链接\n        id_elem = entry.find('atom:id', ns)\n        if id_elem is not None and id_elem.text:\n            paper['arxiv_id'] = id_elem.text.split('/')[-1]\n            paper['link'] = f\"https://arxiv.org/abs/{paper['arxiv_id']}\"\n        else:\n            paper['arxiv_id'] = \"Unknown\"\n            paper['link'] = \"Unknown\"\n        \n        papers.append(paper)\n    \n    print(f\"找到 {len(papers)} 篇相关论文\")\n    print(\"=\" * 80)\n    \n    # 显示论文信息\n    for i, paper in enumerate(papers, 1):\n        print(f\"\\n[{i}] {paper['title']}\")\n        print(f\"作者: {', '.join(paper['authors'][:3])}{'...' if len(paper['authors']) > 3 else ''}\")\n        print(f\"发布日期: {paper['published']}\")\n        print(f\"arXiv ID: {paper['arxiv_id']}\")\n        print(f\"链接: {paper['link']}\")\n        \n        # 显示摘要的前200个字符\n        abstract_preview = paper['abstract'][:200] + \"...\" if len(paper['abstract']) > 200 else paper['abstract']\n        print(f\"摘要: {abstract_preview}\")\n        print(\"-\" * 80)\n    \n    # 保存到文件\n    with open('rag_papers.json', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        json.dump(papers, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    \n    print(f\"\\n论文信息已保存到 rag_papers.json\")\n    \nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"错误: {e}\")\n    print(\"尝试备用方法...\")"}
